      <p class="subtitle">The goal of the project was to make modifying your settings a breeze.</p>

      <p class="lead">We wanted the pages to be more usable, accessible, and visually appealing.</p>

      <p>Perfectly aligned with another project, the settings pages were the prime candidate to accompany the profiles redesign. We wanted to improve the experience of modifying your user and store settings by providing users with a seamless way of transitioning from viewing their profile to editing their profile and settings.</p>
